{"article_id":"PyFjBm0rWCbE83ed","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The death of an American","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"fighting in Syria for the self-declared Islamic State","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"is heightening concerns about the radicalization of US citizens .","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"But some experts say","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"that this case may indicate just the opposite :","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"that the militant group has no immediate interest in US targets .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"Douglas McAuthur McCain of San Diego was killed over the weekend in a battle between rival Syrian rebel groups ,","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"reports NBC News .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"Free Syrian Army sources told NBC","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"that Mr. McCain was fighting alongside IS forces","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"( formerly known as the Islamic State of Iraq and the Levant , or ISIS ) ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"and was identified through both his passport ,","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"which he had been carrying ,","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"and distinctive tattoos .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"Members of McCain 's family in Minneapolis ,","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"where he grew up ,","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"told the Minneapolis Star-Tribune","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"that US officials informed McCain 's mother of his death on Monday .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"Kenyata McCain , a first cousin , said","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"the family is upset and confused over his death and apparent ties to the terrorist group .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"Kenyata McCain said","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"she was in touch with Douglas McCain on Friday ,","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"and \" he was telling all of us","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"he was in Turkey. \"","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"She noted","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"that his Facebook page indicated","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"that he supported the terrorist group ,","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"also known as ISIS .","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"\" I know","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"that he had strong Muslim beliefs , \"","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"she added ,","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"\" but I didn ' t know","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"that he was in support of ISIS .","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"I didn ' t think","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"he would be . \"","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"According to a post on McCain 's Twitter account ,","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"he converted to Islam about 10 years ago ,","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"which he described as `` the best thing","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"that ever happen to me . ''","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"The Washington Post writes","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"that McCain 's radicalization fits the pattern","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"shown by other Westerners","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"who became jihadi fighters ,","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"according to Richard Barrett , a former British intelligence officer","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"now working for the Soufan Group , a security consulting firm .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"Though every Western foreign fighter leaves for Syria for different reasons ,","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"McCain ' s early life carries themes","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"found among other foreign militants .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"They often operate somewhere on the fringes of society","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"and feel excluded ,","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"wrote expert Richard Barrett of the Soufan Group .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"\" The French authorities categorize volunteers from France as disaffected , aimless and lacking a sense of identity or belonging , \"","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"Barrett wrote in his report .","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"\" This appears to be common across most nationalities","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"and fits with the high number of converts ,","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"presumably people","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"who are seeking a greater sense of purpose and meaning in their lives . \"","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"Mr. Barrett also told the Star-Tribune","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"that McCain 's death does not indicate an immediate threat to the US .","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"He notes","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"that McCain 's use as a foot soldier by IS indicates","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"that the group placed no particular value in his American identity ,","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"which could be useful for propaganda","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"or for attacking US targets .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"It `` is further evidence","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"that Americans are going there","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"to fight for ISIS","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"rather than to train as terrorists","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"to attack at home , ''","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"Get the Monitor Stories","depth":5},{"id":71,"text":"you care about","depth":5},{"id":72,"text":"delivered to your inbox .","depth":4},{"id":73,"text":"By signing up ,","depth":4},{"id":74,"text":"you agree to our Privacy Policy","depth":4},{"id":75,"text":"James Gelvin , a professor of Middle East history at the University of California-Los Angeles , told NBC News","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"that the major appeal of IS for disaffected foreigners is that `` they 've been successful '' in Syria and Iraq .","depth":6},{"id":77,"text":"`` They have been able to take territory .","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"Al Qaeda does n't take territory , ''","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":80,"text":"But that very success could eventually drive away Americans and other foreigners ,","depth":5},{"id":81,"text":"because","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"once ISIS takes control in a region ,","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"it cracks down with a severe interpretation of Islam","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"that quickly makes its leaders unpopular .","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"`` Once you get to know them ,","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"you get to hate them , '' [ Mr. ]","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"Gelvin said .","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"While the threat of terrorist-trained Americans ' returning home is a serious concern","depth":6},{"id":89,"text":"- `` of course it is , ''","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"he said -","depth":5},{"id":91,"text":"it 's more likely that any Americans","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"who survive their battles in Iraq and Syria","depth":6},{"id":93,"text":"will return home discouraged and disillusioned , not dangerous .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":187,"left":163,"right":186,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":163,"left":99,"right":162,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":96,"right":98,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":96,"left":95,"right":2,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":95,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":3,"right":97,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":97,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":131,"right":161,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":106,"right":130,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":100,"right":105,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":8,"right":104,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":104,"left":101,"right":103,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":101,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":102,"right":13,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":102,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":111,"right":129,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":111,"lef